snippet.title: Kid Bubblegum | Trailer | Kick Ass And Shoot Bubblegum!
snippet.description:
Aliens have invaded, and Kid Bubblegum is too cool to let that slide. Armed with his trusty Gumslinger, he’ll kick some alien butt and shoot bubblegum…and he has plenty of gum!

Grab the game now:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2441500/Kid_Bubblegum/
Itchio: https://ohsat-andrej.itch.io/kid-bubblegum
